\c 2
\s Ukuzalwa kukaMozisi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusuka indoda yendlu yakoLevi, yathatha indodakazi yakoLevi\x + 6.20. Nani 26.59. 1 Lan. 23.14.\x*.
\v 2 Owesifazana wasethatha isisu, wazala indodana; eseyibonile ukuthi inhle, wayifihla inyanga ezintathu\x + Seb. 7.20. Heb. 11.23.\x*.
\v 3 Kwathi engaselakuyifihla wayithathela isitsha semizi\x + Jobe 8.11. Isa. 18.2; 35.7.\x*, wasibhada ngengcino langethara, wafaka umntwana kuso, wasibeka emihlangeni ekhunjini lomfula\x + 2.5. Isa. 19.6.\x*.
\v 4 Udadewabo\x + 15.20. Nani 26.59.\x* wasezimisa khatshana ukuze azi okuzakwenziwa kuye.
\p
\v 5 Kwasekusehla indodakazi kaFaro uku\add ya\add*geza emfuleni; lamantombazana ayo ahamba eceleni komfula. Isibonile isitsha phakathi kwemihlanga, yathuma incekukazi yayo yasithatha\x + Seb. 7.21.\x*.
\v 6 Kwathi isivula, yabona umntwana, khangela-ke, umfanyana wakhala inyembezi. Yasimhawukela yathi: Lo ngomunye wabafana bamaHebheru.
\v 7 Udadewabo wasesithi endodakazini kaFaro: Ngihambe yini ngiyekubizela umfazi omunyisayo kumaHebherukazi ukuze akumunyisele umfana?
\v 8 Indodakazi kaFaro yasisithi kuye: Hamba. Intombi yasihamba, yabiza unina womfana.
\v 9 Indodakazi kaFaro yasisithi kuye: Thatha uhambe lalo umntwana, ungimunyisele yena; njalo mina ngizakupha iholo lakho. Owesifazana wasemthatha umntwana, wammunyisa.
\v 10 Umfana esekhulile, wamletha endodakazini kaFaro, wasesiba yindodana yayo\x + Seb. 7.21. Heb. 11.24.\x*. Yasisitha ibizo layo \add yathi\add* nguMozisi\f + \fk uMozisi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq owakhutshwa.\f*, yathi: Ngoba ngamkhupha emanzini.
\s Ukubaleka kukaMozisi
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi ngalezonsuku, uMozisi esekhulile, waphuma waya kubafowabo\x + Seb. 7.23,24. Heb. 11.24-26.\x*, wakhangela imithwalo yabo\x + 1.11.\x*; futhi wabona umGibhithe etshaya umHebheru kubafowabo.
\v 12 Wathalaza ngapha langapha; esebonile ukuthi kakulamuntu, wamtshaya umGibhithe, wamfihla etshebetshebeni.
\v 13 Waphuma langosuku lwesibili, khangela-ke, amaHebheru amabili esilwa; wasesithi kowonileyo: Umtshayelani umakhelwane wakho\x + Seb. 7.26-28.\x*?
\v 14 Wasesithi: Ngubani okubeke ube yisiphathamandla\f + \fk isiphathamandla: \fl Heb. \fq indoda, isiphathamandla.\f* lomahluleli phezu kwethu? Wena uzimisele ukungibulala yini njengalokho ubulele umGibhithe? UMozisi wasesesaba wathi: Isibili udaba luyaziwa.
\p
\v 15 Kwathi uFaro eseluzwile udaba, wadinga ukumbulala uMozisi. Kodwa uMozisi wabalekela ubuso bukaFaro\x + Seb. 7.29. Heb. 11.27.\x*, wahlala elizweni leMidiyani; wahlala emthonjeni\x + Gen. 24.11; 29.2.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo umpristi weMidiyani wayelamadodakazi ayisikhombisa; eza\x + Gen. 24.11; 29.10. 1 Sam. 9.11.\x* ukukha\x + 2.19. Zaga 20.5.\x*, agcwalisa imikolo\x + Gen. 30.38,41.\x* ukunathisa umhlambi kayise.
\v 17 Kwasekufika abelusi, bawaxotsha; kodwa uMozisi wasukuma, wawasiza wanathisa umhlambi wawo\x + 2.19. Gen. 29.10.\x*.
\v 18 Lapho efika kuRehuweli\x + Nani 10.29. 3.1; 4.18; 18.1.\x* uyise, wathi: Kungani libuye masinyane kangaka lamuhla?
\v 19 Asesithi: Indoda engumGibhithe isophulile esandleni sabelusi; futhi yasikhela lokusikhela, yanathisa umhlambi.
\v 20 Wasesithi emadodakazini akhe: Kambe ingaphi? Kanti liyitshiyeleni indoda? Ibizeni, ukuze idle isinkwa\x + Gen. 31.54; 43.25.\x*.
\v 21 UMozisi wasevuma ukuhlala lendoda; wasemnika uMozisi uZipora indodakazi yakhe\x + 4.25; 18.2.\x*.
\v 22 Wasezala indodana; wayitha ibizo layo uGereshoma\f + \fk uGereshoma: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq owemzini.\f*, ngoba wathi: Ngangingowemzini elizweni lemzini.
\p
\v 23 Kwasekusithi emva kwalezinsuku ezinengi\x + 7.7. Seb. 7.23,30.\x*, inkosi yeGibhithe yafa. Labantwana bakoIsrayeli babubula ngenxa yobugqili\x + Hlab. 12.5. Lilo 1.4,8,11. Hez. 21.6,7.\x*, bakhala; lokukhala kwabo kwenyukela kuNkulunkulu ngenxa yobugqili\x + Gen. 18.20,21. 3.9. Jak. 5.4.\x*.
\v 24 UNkulunkulu wasesizwa ukububula kwabo\x + 6.5.\x*, uNkulunkulu wakhumbula isivumelwano\x + 6.5. Hlab. 105.8,42; 106.45.\x* sakhe loAbrahama, loIsaka, njalo loJakobe\x + Gen. 15.14; 46.4.\x*.
\v 25 UNkulunkulu wasebona abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 3.7; 4.31. 1 Sam. 1.11. 2 Sam. 16.12. Luka 1.25.\x*, uNkulunkulu wa\add ba\add*zi\x + 1.8. Dute. 33.9. 1 Lan. 28.9. Hlab. 1.6; 31.7.\x*.